Date: 1996-03-25

Title: O(d,d,Z) Transformations as Automorphisms of the Operator Algebra

Authors: Ioannis Giannakis (Rockefeller University)

Comments: 9 pages, Plain Tex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B388 (1996) 543-549

We implement the O(d,d,Z) transformations of T-duality as automorphismsof the operator algebras of Conformal Field Theories. This extends thesetransformations to arbitrary field configurations in the deformation class.